In the Matter of the Arbitration between NTA, Inc., Respondent, and Tableau Television, Ltd. et al., Appellants.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the petitioner-respondent. No opinion. Concur — Breitel, J. P., Rabin, M. M. Prank, McNally and Stevens, JJ. [11 Misc 2d 333.]
